title: The Bad Seed TPB
description: Christine Penmark seems to have it all: a lovely home, a loving husband and the most "perfect" daughter in the world. But since childhood, Christine has suffered from the most terrible recurring nightmare. And her "perfect" daughter&#039;s accomplishments include lying, theft and possibly much, much worse. Only Christine knows the truth about her daughter and only Christine&#039;s father knows the truth about her nightmare.
